ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectGerry Byrne - MP Travel to Kaliningrad, Russian Federation
PrecisOrder authorizing Hon. GERRY BYRNE, Member of Parliament, to travel on behalf of the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans to KALININGRAD, RUSSIAN FEDEATION from June 2 to June 6, 2009, to be part of the delegation at the 14th North Atlantic Fisheries Ministers Conference.
